{"title":"老当益壮， 宁移白首之心？","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":64,"url":"https://acm.uestc.edu.cn/problem/lao-dang-yi-zhuang-zhu-yi-bai-shou-zhi-xin/description","statement":[{"title":"Content","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"\n请构造一个01串，使其满足以下条件：\n\n+ 环状（即首尾相连）\n+ 每一位取值为0或1\n+ 长度是$2^n$\n+ 对于每个($2^n$个)位置，从其开始沿逆时针方向的连续的n位01串（包括自己）构成的数均不相同，即0到$2^n-1$中的数各出现一次\n"},{"title":"Standard Input","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"\n输入一个整数$n(1\\le n \\le 15)$\n"},{"title":"Standard Output","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"\n输出任一一个长度为$2^n$且满足题意的01串（顺逆时针均可），保证输入有解。\n"},{"title":"Samples","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<style>\n        table,table tr th, table tr td { border:1px solid #0094ff; }\n        table { width: 200px; min-height: 25px; line-height: 25px; text-align: center; border-collapse: collapse;}   \n    </style>\n<table>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td>Input</td>\n\t\t<td>Output</td>\n\t</tr>\n<tr><td>3</td><td>00010111</td></tr></table>\n\n"},{"title":"Note","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"\n样例的$00010111$,对于每个位置，沿逆时针方向连续长度为3的01串有：$000, 001, 010, 101, 011, 111, 110, 100$,即为$0-7$的所有数字\n"}]}